{"tid":409634,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《一念無明》代表香港爭奧斯卡最佳外語片！！！","createTime":"2017-09-22T08:32:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-22T23:22:51.000Z","uid":14730,"like":13,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"303250252ad9ecd21a3dc7de59d3ba05f2ec7839","tid":409634,"uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T08:32:04.000Z","msg":"香港電影製片家協會董事局推薦余文樂、曾志偉、金燕玲主演的電影《一念無明》代表香港角逐第90屆奧斯卡金像獎最佳外語片獎。<br />\n<br />\n是次推選，香港電影製片家協會董事局成員從2016年10月至2017年9月期間上映的香港電影中挑選，從最後4部影片包括《追龍》、《擺渡人》、《七月與安生》及《一念無明》中，選出《一念無明》代表香港參加角逐。<br />\n<br />\nsources：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2xszMhI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2xszMhI&d=w4d6%2BSG2rwswpfweG4w1KdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=5d7ca4c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2xszMhI</a>"},{"pid":"a605193804023723f2838a4170b5252132c65a3d","tid":409634,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T09:53:57.000Z","msg":"《追龍》<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n《擺渡人》<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9819f95174c35b037ffd373c8c0b74f1d6a0656a","tid":409634,"uid":56467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T10:34:50.000Z","msg":"擺渡人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68cf1365cb94ba7f555d8dd86f97c8fc7e1af052","tid":409634,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T10:45:57.000Z"